Output demo/scan.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Padding 18
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "cd /Users/amsrahman/waqwaq && clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 700ms
Type "waqwaq scan . /tmp/arch"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "waqwaq toc /tmp/arch | head"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2.2s

Type "waqwaq cat internal/store /tmp/arch | head -18"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s
